    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>20th-level Oath of Glory feature</i></p><p>You can empower yourself with the legends—whether true or exaggerated—of your great deeds. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 minute:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You are blessed with an otherworldly presence, gaining advantage on all Charisma checks.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Once on each of your turns when you make a weapon attack and miss, you can cause that attack to hit instead.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">If you fail a saving throw, you can use your reaction to reroll it. You must use this new roll.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div>",
